	(text "INPUT SECTION\n\nSignal flow:\n1. J1 XLR pins 2,3 → R_ph1/R_ph2 (6.81K 0.1%) → +48V phantom (SW_48V)\n2. → R_pad1/R_pad2 (649R) via SW_PAD (DPST) → bypass when OFF\n3. → T1 JT-115K-E primary (HOT pin 1, COLD pin 3)\n4. T1 secondary: S_HOT (pin 4) → Signal Rail\n5. Termination: R_term(13.7K) + C_term(680pF) + R_30K(30.1K) across secondary\n\nUse symbol JT-115K-E from TripleTopoCustom library"
		(at 25.4 25.4 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.524 1.524)) (justify left))
		(uuid "f3000001-inpt-text-0003-000000000001")
	)
